I am a medical doctor, graduated from New Zealand, currently undertaking an
M.Phil. in International Relations at the University of Cambridge in the UK.
As part of this course I have chosen to write my M.Phil. thesis on the
institutional responses to the emerging infectious diseases, in particular
looking at international cooperation on the issue. Unfortunately as I am in
graduate accomodation and in the UK I have not been able to see the below
mentioned documentary, but would be absolutely fascinated to do so.
Could you please be so kind as to assist me on how I could obtain a copy of
the report, or if it will be screened on British television in the near
future.
