From: DAVID W. HAUSE <hause@EMAIL.AFIP.OSD.MIL>
More on the phone number which Phyllis found: They identified themselves as
a clearing house and referred me to a second number, 1-800-672-6202, which is
answered as Warner Home Videos; WHV told me they do not ship outside the US,
and they do not have a standard 'you-pay-the-charge' phone number. (My
previous experience is that, at least from Germany, you can't direct-dial a
US toll free (800 or 888) number.) Maybe some embassy/consulate health
officers in the US will volunteer to help their compatriots?
